msgid ""
"Select how often a compressed copy of the data will be made. <br />Archive path <code>/usr/lib/easyconfig/easyconfig_statistics.json.gz</code>. <br /><br /><b>Important</b> <br />Please "
"remember that frequent write operations shorten the life cycle of memory."
msgstr ""
"Vælg, hvor ofte der skal oprettes en komprimeret kopi af dataene. <br />Arkivsti <code>/usr/lib/easyconfig/easyconfig_statistics.json.gz</code>. <br /><br /><b>Vigtigt</b> <br />Husk, "
"at hyppige skriveoperationer forkorter hukommelsens levetid."

msgid ""
"Enable transfer data collection. <br />Data is saved to file <code>/tmp/easyconfig_statistics.json</code>. <br /><br /><b>What you should know</b> <br />With "
"flow offloading enabled, transfer data will be inconsistent with reality or may be completely unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver indsamling af overførselsdata. <br />Data gemmes i filen <code>/tmp/easyconfig_statistics.json</code>. <br /><br /><b>Hvad du bør vide</b> <br />Når "
"flow offloading er aktiveret, vil overførselsdata være inkonsistente med virkeligheden eller kan være helt utilgængelige."

